 CANNELLONIS DE KUZU 

00:00:19.690 --> 00:00:23.490
 Ingredients: - 20 g Culinary Journey Vegetable Fund - 500 g Water - 80 g Promochi (Kuzu) Sosa - Water QS - Salt QS - Chilli QS 

00:00:23.650 --> 00:00:27.290
 For the vegetable stuffing: - 200 g Vegetables cut in fine brunoise - 3 g of Gelburger Sosa gelling agent - 10 g of vegetable broth 

00:00:27.450 --> 00:00:30.050
 For the sauce: - 100 g Vegetable broth - 1 g Xantana Clear Sosa Thickener 

00:00:33.850 --> 00:00:56.810
 Mix all the ingredients and bring to a boil without stirring. 

00:00:59.370 --> 00:01:07.730
 Work the dough until it comes off the sides of the pan. 

00:01:08.850 --> 00:01:13.790
 Place the dough between two silicone mats and roll it out with a rolling pin until you have a very fine dough. 

00:01:18.290 --> 00:01:24.130
 Let stand in the refrigerator for 2 hours. 

